    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s analog masterpiece. At its heart is the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual and a variable M-differential lock. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and structural reinforcement of the rear subframe. The chassis remains taut with upgraded polyurethane bushings and refreshed dampers, ensuring the legendary 50/50 weight distribution is fully exploited. While the finish shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain remains robust and free of leaks, offering a visceral, high-revving performance profile for the discerning pilot.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
