      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously cared for and remains in impressive condition. The exterior boasts a deep, vibrant finish with only the minor, expected road wear consistent with a well-loved daily driver. Inside, you\u2019ll find a pristine, smoke-free cabin where the upholstery remains supple and all electronic components\u2014from the infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014function exactly as they should. Mechanically, the car is sound; it has followed a strict maintenance schedule, with recent service including a fresh oil change and a comprehensive brake inspection. The engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts with precision, offering a reliable and engaging driving experience. Complete with a full set of service records and two keys, this car is ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately without any looming maintenance concerns.",
